[
  {
    "bookname": "Jeremiah",
    "chapter": "6",
    "text": "<p class=\"poetry\">\u201c<st data-num=\"05756\" class=\"\">Run for safety</st>, <st data-num=\"01121\" class=\"\">people</st> of <st data-num=\"01144\" class=\"\">Benjamin</st>!<p class=\"poetry\">Get <st data-num=\"07130\" class=\"\">out of</st> <st data-num=\"03389\" class=\"\">Jerusalem</st>!<n id=\"1\" /> <p class=\"poetry\"><st data-num=\"08628\" class=\"\">Sound</st> the <st data-num=\"07782\" class=\"\">trumpet</st><n id=\"2\" /> in <st data-num=\"08620\" class=\"\">Tekoa</st>!<p class=\"poetry\"><st data-num=\"05375\" class=\"\">Light</st> the <st data-num=\"04864\" class=\"\">signal fires</st> <st data-num=\"05921\" class=\"\">at</st> <st data-num=\"01021\" class=\"\">Beth Hakkerem</st>!<p class=\"poetry\"><st data-num=\"03588\" class=\"\">For</st> <st data-num=\"07451\" class=\"\">disaster</st> <st data-num=\"08259\" class=\"\">lurks</st><n id=\"3\" /> out of the <st data-num=\"06828\" class=\"\">north</st>;<p class=\"poetry\">it will bring <st data-num=\"01419\" class=\"\">great</st> <st data-num=\"07667\" class=\"\">destruction</st>.<n id=\"4\" /> </p>",
    "verse": "1"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "Jeremiah",
    "chapter": "6",
    "text": "<p class=\"poetry\">I will <st data-num=\"01820\" class=\"\">destroy</st><n id=\"1\" /> <st data-num=\"01323\" class=\"\">Daughter</st> <st data-num=\"06726\" class=\"\">Zion</st>,<n id=\"2\" /> <p class=\"poetry\">who is as <st data-num=\"05000\" class=\"\">delicate</st> and <st data-num=\"06026\" class=\"\">defenseless</st> as a young maiden.<n id=\"3\" /> </p>",
    "verse": "2"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "Jeremiah",
    "chapter": "6",
    "text": "<p class=\"poetry\"><st data-num=\"07462\" class=\"\">Kings</st> will <st data-num=\"0413 0935\">attack</st> her with their <st data-num=\"05739\" class=\"\">armies</st>.<n id=\"1\" /> <p class=\"poetry\">They will <st data-num=\"08628 0168\">encamp</st> <st data-num=\"05921\" class=\"\">in siege</st> <st data-num=\"05439\" class=\"\">all around</st> her.<n id=\"2\" /> <p class=\"poetry\"><st data-num=\"0376\" class=\"\">Each</st> of them will <st data-num=\"07462\" class=\"\">devastate</st> the <st data-num=\"03027\" class=\"\">portion</st> assigned to him.<n id=\"3\" /></p>",
    "verse": "3"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "Jeremiah",
    "chapter": "6",
    "text": "<p class=\"poetry\">They will say,<n id=\"1\" /> \u2018<st data-num=\"06942\" class=\"\">Prepare</st> to do <st data-num=\"04421\" class=\"\">battle</st><n id=\"2\" /> <st data-num=\"05921\" class=\"\">against</st> it!<p class=\"poetry\"><st data-num=\"06965\" class=\"\">Come on</st>! Let\u2019s <st data-num=\"05927\" class=\"\">attack</st> it at <st data-num=\"06672\" class=\"\">noon</st>!\u2019<p class=\"poetry\">But later they will say,<n id=\"3\" /> \u2018<st data-num=\"0188\">Woe</st> to us!<n id=\"4\" /> <p class=\"poetry\"><st data-num=\"03588\">For</st> the <st data-num=\"03117\" class=\"\">day</st> <st data-num=\"06437\" class=\"\">is almost over</st>,<p class=\"poetry\">and the <st data-num=\"06752\" class=\"\">shadows</st> of <st data-num=\"06153\" class=\"\">evening</st> are <st data-num=\"05186\" class=\"\">getting long</st>.</p>",
    "verse": "4"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "Jeremiah",
    "chapter": "6",
    "text": "<p class=\"poetry\">So <st data-num=\"06965\" class=\"\">come on</st>, let\u2019s <st data-num=\"05927\" class=\"\">go ahead and attack</st> it by <st data-num=\"03915\" class=\"\">night</st><p class=\"poetry\">and <st data-num=\"07843\" class=\"\">destroy</st> all its <st data-num=\"0759\" class=\"\">fortified buildings</st>.\u2019 </p>",
    "verse": "5"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "Jeremiah",
    "chapter": "6",
    "text": "<p class=\"poetry\">All this is <st data-num=\"03588\" class=\"\">because</st><n id=\"1\" /> the <span class=\"smcaps\"><st data-num=\"03068\" class=\"\">Lord</st></span> of <st data-num=\"06635\">Heaven\u2019s Armies</st><n id=\"2\" /> has <st data-num=\"03541 0559\">said</st>:<p class=\"poetry\">\u2018<st data-num=\"03772\" class=\"\">Cut down</st> the <st data-num=\"06097\" class=\"\">trees</st> <st data-num=\"05921\" class=\"\">around</st> <st data-num=\"03389\" class=\"\">Jerusalem</st><p class=\"poetry\">and <st data-num=\"08210\" class=\"\">build up</st> a <st data-num=\"05550\" class=\"\">siege ramp</st> against its walls.<n id=\"3\" /> <p class=\"poetry\"><st data-num=\"01931\" class=\"\">This</st> is the <st data-num=\"05892\" class=\"\">city</st> that is to be <st data-num=\"06485\" class=\"\">punished</st>.<n id=\"4\" /> <p class=\"poetry\"><st data-num=\"03605\" class=\"\">Nothing but</st> <st data-num=\"06233\" class=\"\">oppression</st> happens in <st data-num=\"07130\" class=\"\">it</st>.<n id=\"5\" /> </p>",
    "verse": "6"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "Jeremiah",
    "chapter": "6",
    "text": "<p class=\"poetry\">As a <st data-num=\"0875\">well</st> continually <st data-num=\"06979\" class=\"\">pours out</st> <st data-num=\"04325\" class=\"\">fresh water</st>,<p class=\"poetry\"><st data-num=\"03651\" class=\"\">so</st> it continually <st data-num=\"06979\" class=\"\">pours out</st> <st data-num=\"07451\" class=\"\">wicked deeds</st>.<n id=\"1\" /> <p class=\"poetry\">Sounds of <st data-num=\"02555\" class=\"\">violence</st> and <st data-num=\"07701\" class=\"\">destruction</st> <st data-num=\"08085\" class=\"\">echo</st> throughout it.<n id=\"2\" /> <p class=\"poetry\"><st data-num=\"08548\" class=\"\">All</st> I <st data-num=\"05921 06440\">see</st> are <st data-num=\"02483\" class=\"\">sick</st> and <st data-num=\"04347\" class=\"\">wounded</st> people.\u2019<n id=\"3\" /></p>",
    "verse": "7"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "Jeremiah",
    "chapter": "6",
    "text": "<p class=\"poetry\">So<n id=\"1\" /> <st data-num=\"03256\" class=\"\">take warning</st>, <st data-num=\"03389\" class=\"\">Jerusalem</st>,<p class=\"poetry\"><st data-num=\"06435\" class=\"\">or</st> <st data-num=\"05315\" class=\"\">I</st> will <st data-num=\"03363 04480\">abandon</st> you <st data-num=\"03363 04480\">in disgust</st><n id=\"2\" /> <p class=\"poetry\"><st data-num=\"06435\" class=\"\">and</st> <st data-num=\"07760\" class=\"\">make</st> you <st data-num=\"08077\" class=\"\">desolate</st>,<p class=\"poetry\">a <st data-num=\"0776\" class=\"\">place</st> where <st data-num=\"03808\" class=\"\">no</st> one can <st data-num=\"03427\" class=\"\">live</st>.\u201d </p>",
    "verse": "8"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "Jeremiah",
    "chapter": "6",
    "text": "<p class=\"bodytext\"><st data-num=\"03541\" class=\"\">This is what</st> the <span class=\"smcaps\"><st data-num=\"03068\" class=\"\">Lord</st></span> of <st data-num=\"03068\">Heaven\u2019s Armies</st><n id=\"1\" /> <st data-num=\"0559\" class=\"\">said</st> to me:<n id=\"2\" /> <p class=\"poetry\">\u201cThose who <st data-num=\"07611\" class=\"\">remain</st> in <st data-num=\"03478\" class=\"\">Israel</st> will be <p class=\"poetry\">like the <st data-num=\"01612\" class=\"\">grapes</st> <st data-num=\"05953\" class=\"\">thoroughly</st> <st data-num=\"05953\" class=\"\">gleaned</st><n id=\"3\" /> <st data-num=\"01612\" class=\"\">from a vine</st>.<p class=\"poetry\">So go over them <st data-num=\"07725\" class=\"\">again</st>, as though you were a <st data-num=\"01219\" class=\"\">grape harvester</st><p class=\"poetry\"><st data-num=\"07725\" class=\"\">passing</st> your <st data-num=\"03027\" class=\"\">hand</st> <st data-num=\"05921\" class=\"\">over</st> the <st data-num=\"05552\" class=\"\">branches</st> one last time.\u201d<n id=\"4\" /></p>",
    "verse": "9"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "Jeremiah",
    "chapter": "6",
    "text": "<p class=\"bodytext\">I answered,<n id=\"1\" /> <p class=\"poetry\">\u201c<st data-num=\"04310\" class=\"\">Who</st> would <st data-num=\"08085\" class=\"\">listen</st><p class=\"poetry\">if I <st data-num=\"01696\" class=\"\">spoke</st> <st data-num=\"05921\" class=\"\">to</st> them and <st data-num=\"05749\" class=\"\">warned</st> them?<n id=\"2\" /> <p class=\"poetry\">Their <st data-num=\"0241\" class=\"\">ears</st> are <st data-num=\"02009\" class=\"\">so</st> <st data-num=\"06189\" class=\"\">closed</st><n id=\"3\" /> <p class=\"poetry\">that they <st data-num=\"03808 03201\">cannot</st> <st data-num=\"07181\" class=\"\">hear</st>!<p class=\"poetry\"><st data-num=\"02009\" class=\"\">Indeed</st>,<n id=\"4\" /> the <span class=\"smcaps\"><st data-num=\"03068\" class=\"\">Lord</st></span>\u2019s <st data-num=\"01697\" class=\"\">message</st> <st data-num=\"01961\" class=\"\">is</st> <st data-num=\"02781\" class=\"\">offensive</st> to them.<p class=\"poetry\">They do <st data-num=\"03808\" class=\"\">not</st> <st data-num=\"02654\" class=\"\">like</st> it at all.<n id=\"5\" /></p>",
    "verse": "10"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "Jeremiah",
    "chapter": "6",
    "text": "<p class=\"poetry\">I <st data-num=\"04392\" class=\"\">am</st> as <st data-num=\"04392\" class=\"\">full</st> <st data-num=\"0854\" class=\"\">of</st> <st data-num=\"02534\" class=\"\">anger</st> as you are, <span class=\"smcaps\"><st data-num=\"03068\" class=\"\">Lord</st></span>.<n id=\"1\" /> <p class=\"poetry\">I <st data-num=\"03811\" class=\"\">am tired</st> of trying to <st data-num=\"03557\" class=\"\">hold</st> it <st data-num=\"03557\" class=\"\">in</st>.\u201d<p class=\"bodytext\">The <span class=\"smcaps\">Lord</span> answered,<n id=\"2\" /> <p class=\"poetry\">\u201c<st data-num=\"08210\" class=\"\">Vent</st> it, then,<n id=\"3\" /> <st data-num=\"05921\" class=\"\">on</st> the <st data-num=\"05768\" class=\"\">children</st> who play in the <st data-num=\"02351\" class=\"\">street</st><p class=\"poetry\">and <st data-num=\"05921\" class=\"\">on</st> the <st data-num=\"0970\" class=\"\">young men</st> who are <st data-num=\"05475\" class=\"\">gathered</st> <st data-num=\"03162\" class=\"\">together</st>.<p class=\"poetry\"><st data-num=\"0376\" class=\"\">Husbands</st> <st data-num=\"05973\" class=\"\">and</st> <st data-num=\"0802\" class=\"\">wives</st> are to be <st data-num=\"01571 03920\">included</st>,<n id=\"4\" /> <p class=\"poetry\">as well as the <st data-num=\"02205\" class=\"\">old</st> <st data-num=\"05973\" class=\"\">and</st> those who are <st data-num=\"04390\" class=\"\">advanced</st> in <st data-num=\"03117\" class=\"\">years</st>. </p>",
    "verse": "11"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "Jeremiah",
    "chapter": "6",
    "text": "<p class=\"poetry\">Their <st data-num=\"01004\" class=\"\">houses</st> will be <st data-num=\"05437\" class=\"\">turned over</st> to <st data-num=\"0312\" class=\"\">others</st><p class=\"poetry\"><st data-num=\"03162\" class=\"\">as</st> will their <st data-num=\"07704\" class=\"\">fields</st> and their <st data-num=\"0802\" class=\"\">wives</st>.<p class=\"poetry\"><st data-num=\"03588\" class=\"\">For</st> I will <st data-num=\"05186\" class=\"\">unleash</st> my <st data-num=\"03027\" class=\"\">power</st><n id=\"1\" /> <p class=\"poetry\"><st data-num=\"05921\" class=\"\">against</st> those who <st data-num=\"03427\" class=\"\">live</st> in this <st data-num=\"0776\" class=\"\">land</st>,\u201d<p class=\"poetry\"><st data-num=\"05002\" class=\"\">says</st> the <span class=\"smcaps\"><st data-num=\"03068\" class=\"\">Lord</st></span>. </p>",
    "verse": "12"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "Jeremiah",
    "chapter": "6",
    "text": "<p class=\"poetry\">\u201cThat is <st data-num=\"03588\" class=\"\">because</st>, from the <st data-num=\"06996\" class=\"\">least important</st> <st data-num=\"05704\" class=\"\">to</st> the <st data-num=\"01419\" class=\"\">most important</st> of them,<p class=\"poetry\"><st data-num=\"03605\" class=\"\">all</st> of them <st data-num=\"01214\" class=\"\">are greedy</st> for <st data-num=\"01215\" class=\"\">dishonest gain</st>.<p class=\"poetry\"><st data-num=\"05030\" class=\"\">Prophets</st> and <st data-num=\"03548\" class=\"\">priests</st> <st data-num=\"05704\" class=\"\">alike</st>,<p class=\"poetry\"><st data-num=\"03605\" class=\"\">all</st> of them <st data-num=\"06213\" class=\"\">practice</st> <st data-num=\"08267\" class=\"\">deceit</st>. </p>",
    "verse": "13"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "Jeremiah",
    "chapter": "6",
    "text": "<p class=\"poetry\">They <st data-num=\"07495\" class=\"\">offer</st> <st data-num=\"05921\" class=\"\">only</st> <st data-num=\"07043\" class=\"\">superficial</st> <st data-num=\"07495\" class=\"\">help</st> <p class=\"poetry\">for the <st data-num=\"07667\" class=\"\">harm</st> my <st data-num=\"05971\" class=\"\">people</st> have suffered.<n id=\"1\" /> <p class=\"poetry\">They <st data-num=\"0559\" class=\"\">say</st>, \u2018<st data-num=\"07965\" class=\"\">Everything</st> will be <st data-num=\"07965\" class=\"\">all right</st>!\u2019<p class=\"poetry\">But everything <st data-num=\"0369\" class=\"\">is not</st> <st data-num=\"07965\" class=\"\">all right</st>!<n id=\"2\" /> </p>",
    "verse": "14"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "Jeremiah",
    "chapter": "6",
    "text": "<p class=\"poetry\">Are they <st data-num=\"03001\" class=\"\">ashamed</st> <st data-num=\"03588\" class=\"\">because</st> they have <st data-num=\"06213\" class=\"\">done</st> such <st data-num=\"08441\" class=\"\">shameful things</st>?<p class=\"poetry\"><st data-num=\"01571\" class=\"\">No</st>, they are <st data-num=\"03808\" class=\"\">not</st> <st data-num=\"0954\" class=\"\">at all</st> <st data-num=\"0954\" class=\"\">ashamed</st>.<p class=\"poetry\">They do <st data-num=\"03808\" class=\"\">not</st> <st data-num=\"01571\" class=\"\">even</st> <st data-num=\"03045\" class=\"\">know how</st> to <st data-num=\"03637\" class=\"\">blush</st>!<p class=\"poetry\"><st data-num=\"03651\" class=\"\">So</st> they will <st data-num=\"05307\" class=\"\">die</st>, just like others have <st data-num=\"05307\" class=\"\">died</st>.<n id=\"1\" /> <p class=\"poetry\">They will <st data-num=\"03782\" class=\"\">be brought to ruin</st> <st data-num=\"06256\" class=\"\">when</st> I <st data-num=\"06485\" class=\"\">punish</st> them,\u201d<p class=\"poetry\"><st data-num=\"0559\" class=\"\">says</st> the <span class=\"smcaps\"><st data-num=\"03068\" class=\"\">Lord</st></span>. </p>",
    "verse": "15"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "Jeremiah",
    "chapter": "6",
    "text": "<p class=\"bodytext\">The <span class=\"smcaps\"><st data-num=\"03068\" class=\"\">Lord</st></span> <st data-num=\"03541 0559\">said</st> to his people:<n id=\"1\" /> <p class=\"poetry\">\u201cYou are <st data-num=\"05975\" class=\"\">standing</st> <st data-num=\"05921\" class=\"\">at</st> the <st data-num=\"01870\" class=\"\">crossroads</st>. So <st data-num=\"07200\" class=\"\">consider</st> your path.<n id=\"2\" /> <p class=\"poetry\"><st data-num=\"07592\" class=\"\">Ask</st> where the <st data-num=\"05769\" class=\"\">old</st>, <st data-num=\"05410\" class=\"\">reliable paths</st><n id=\"3\" /> are.<p class=\"poetry\">Ask <st data-num=\"0335\" class=\"\">where</st> <st data-num=\"02088\" class=\"\">the</st> <st data-num=\"01870\" class=\"\">path</st> is that leads to <st data-num=\"02896\" class=\"\">blessing</st><n id=\"4\" /> and <st data-num=\"01980\" class=\"\">follow</st> it.<p class=\"poetry\">If you do, you will <st data-num=\"04672\" class=\"\">find</st> <st data-num=\"04771\" class=\"\">rest</st> for your <st data-num=\"05315\" class=\"\">souls</st>.\u201d<p class=\"poetry\">But they <st data-num=\"0559\" class=\"\">said</st>, \u201cWe will <st data-num=\"03808\" class=\"\">not</st> <st data-num=\"01980\" class=\"\">follow</st> it!\u201d</p>",
    "verse": "16"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "Jeremiah",
    "chapter": "6",
    "text": "<p class=\"bodytext\">The <span class=\"smcaps\">Lord</span> said,<n id=\"1\" /> <p class=\"poetry\">\u201cI <st data-num=\"06965\" class=\"\">appointed</st> prophets as <st data-num=\"06822\" class=\"\">watchmen</st> <st data-num=\"05921\" class=\"\">to warn</st> you,<n id=\"2\" /> saying,<p class=\"poetry\">\u2018<st data-num=\"07181\" class=\"\">Pay attention</st> to the warning <st data-num=\"06963\" class=\"\">sound</st> of the <st data-num=\"07782\" class=\"\">trumpet</st>!\u2019\u201d<n id=\"3\" /> <p class=\"poetry\">But they <st data-num=\"0559\" class=\"\">said</st>, \u201cWe will <st data-num=\"03808\" class=\"\">not</st> <st data-num=\"07181\" class=\"\">pay attention</st>!\u201d </p>",
    "verse": "17"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "Jeremiah",
    "chapter": "6",
    "text": "<p class=\"bodytext\"><st data-num=\"03651\" class=\"\">So</st> the <span class=\"smcaps\">Lord</span> said,<n id=\"1\" /> <p class=\"poetry\">\u201c<st data-num=\"08085\" class=\"\">Hear</st>, you <st data-num=\"01471\" class=\"\">nations</st>!<p class=\"poetry\">Be <st data-num=\"05713\" class=\"\">witnesses</st> and <st data-num=\"03045\" class=\"\">take note of</st> <st data-num=\"0834\" class=\"\">what</st> will happen to these people.<n id=\"2\" /></p>",
    "verse": "18"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "Jeremiah",
    "chapter": "6",
    "text": "<p class=\"poetry\"><st data-num=\"08085\" class=\"\">Hear</st> this, you peoples of the <st data-num=\"0776\" class=\"\">earth</st>:<n id=\"1\" /> <p class=\"poetry\">\u2018<st data-num=\"02009\" class=\"\">Take note</st>!<n id=\"2\" /> <st data-num=\"0595\" class=\"\">I</st> am about to <st data-num=\"0935\" class=\"\">bring</st> <st data-num=\"07451\" class=\"\">disaster</st> <st data-num=\"0413\" class=\"\">on</st> <st data-num=\"02088\" class=\"\">these</st> <st data-num=\"05971\" class=\"\">people</st>.<p class=\"poetry\">It will come as <st data-num=\"06529\" class=\"\">punishment</st> for their <st data-num=\"04284\" class=\"\">scheming</st>.<n id=\"3\" /> <p class=\"poetry\"><st data-num=\"03588\" class=\"\">For</st> they have <st data-num=\"07181\" class=\"\">paid</st> <st data-num=\"03808\" class=\"\">no</st> <st data-num=\"07181\" class=\"\">attention</st> <st data-num=\"05921\" class=\"\">to</st> <st data-num=\"01697\" class=\"\">what</st> I have <st data-num=\"01697\" class=\"\">said</st>,<n id=\"4\" /> <p class=\"poetry\">and they have <st data-num=\"03988\" class=\"\">rejected</st> my <st data-num=\"08451\" class=\"\">law</st>. </p>",
    "verse": "19"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "Jeremiah",
    "chapter": "6",
    "text": "<p class=\"poetry\">I <st data-num=\"04100 02088\">take no delight</st><n id=\"1\" /> when they offer up to me<n id=\"2\" /> <p class=\"poetry\"><st data-num=\"03828\" class=\"\">frankincense</st> that <st data-num=\"0935\" class=\"\">comes</st> from <st data-num=\"07614\" class=\"\">Sheba</st> <p class=\"poetry\">or <st data-num=\"02896\" class=\"\">sweet-smelling</st> <st data-num=\"07070\" class=\"\">cane</st> imported from a <st data-num=\"04801\" class=\"\">faraway</st> <st data-num=\"0776\" class=\"\">land</st>.<p class=\"poetry\">I <st data-num=\"03808\" class=\"\">cannot</st> <st data-num=\"07522\" class=\"\">accept</st> the <st data-num=\"05930\" class=\"\">burnt offerings</st> they bring me.<p class=\"poetry\">I <st data-num=\"06149\" class=\"\">get</st> <st data-num=\"03808\" class=\"\">no</st> <st data-num=\"06149\" class=\"\">pleasure</st> from the <st data-num=\"02077\" class=\"\">sacrifices</st> they offer to me.\u2019\u201d<n id=\"3\" /></p>",
    "verse": "20"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "Jeremiah",
    "chapter": "6",
    "text": "<p class=\"bodytext\"><st data-num=\"03651\" class=\"\">So</st>, <st data-num=\"03541\" class=\"\">this is what</st> the <span class=\"smcaps\"><st data-num=\"03068\" class=\"\">Lord</st></span> <st data-num=\"0559\" class=\"\">says</st>:<p class=\"poetry\">\u201cI will <st data-num=\"02005\" class=\"\">assuredly</st><n id=\"1\" /> <st data-num=\"05414 0413\">make</st> <st data-num=\"02088\" class=\"\">these</st> <st data-num=\"05971\" class=\"\">people</st> <st data-num=\"04383\" class=\"\">stumble to</st> their <st data-num=\"04383\" class=\"\">doom</st>.<n id=\"2\" /> <p class=\"poetry\"><st data-num=\"01\" class=\"\">Parents</st> and <st data-num=\"01121\" class=\"\">children</st> will <st data-num=\"03782\" class=\"\">stumble and fall to</st> their <st data-num=\"03782\" class=\"\">destruction</st>.<n id=\"3\" /> <p class=\"poetry\"><st data-num=\"07453\" class=\"\">Friends</st> and <st data-num=\"07934\" class=\"\">neighbors</st> will <st data-num=\"06\" class=\"\">die</st>.\u201d </p>",
    "verse": "21"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "Jeremiah",
    "chapter": "6",
    "text": "<p class=\"bodytext\"><st data-num=\"03541\" class=\"\">This is what</st> the <span class=\"smcaps\"><st data-num=\"03068\" class=\"\">Lord</st></span> <st data-num=\"0559\" class=\"\">says</st>:<p class=\"poetry\">\u201c<st data-num=\"02009\" class=\"\">Beware</st>! An <st data-num=\"05971\" class=\"\">army</st><n id=\"1\" /> is <st data-num=\"0935\" class=\"\">coming</st> from a <st data-num=\"0776\" class=\"\">land</st> in the <st data-num=\"06828\" class=\"\">north</st>.<p class=\"poetry\">A <st data-num=\"01419\" class=\"\">mighty</st> <st data-num=\"01471\" class=\"\">nation</st> is <st data-num=\"05782\" class=\"\">stirring into action</st> in <st data-num=\"03411\" class=\"\">faraway parts</st> of the <st data-num=\"0776\" class=\"\">earth</st>. </p>",
    "verse": "22"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "Jeremiah",
    "chapter": "6",
    "text": "<p class=\"poetry\">Its soldiers <st data-num=\"02388\" class=\"\">are armed</st> with <st data-num=\"07198\" class=\"\">bows</st> and <st data-num=\"03591\" class=\"\">spears</st>.<p class=\"poetry\"><st data-num=\"01931\" class=\"\">They</st> are <st data-num=\"0394\" class=\"\">cruel</st> and <st data-num=\"07355\" class=\"\">show</st> <st data-num=\"03808\" class=\"\">no</st> <st data-num=\"07355\" class=\"\">mercy</st>.<p class=\"poetry\">They <st data-num=\"06963\" class=\"\">sound</st> like the <st data-num=\"01993\" class=\"\">roaring</st> <st data-num=\"03220\" class=\"\">sea</st><p class=\"poetry\">as they <st data-num=\"07392\" class=\"\">ride forth</st> <st data-num=\"05921\" class=\"\">on</st> their <st data-num=\"05483\" class=\"\">horses</st>.<p class=\"poetry\"><st data-num=\"06186\" class=\"\">Lined up in formation</st> like <st data-num=\"0376\" class=\"\">men</st> going into <st data-num=\"04421\" class=\"\">battle</st><p class=\"poetry\"><st data-num=\"05921\" class=\"\">to attack</st> you, <st data-num=\"01323\" class=\"\">Daughter</st> <st data-num=\"06726\" class=\"\">Zion</st>.\u201d<n id=\"1\" /> </p>",
    "verse": "23"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "Jeremiah",
    "chapter": "6",
    "text": "<p class=\"poetry\">The people cry out,<n id=\"1\" /> \u201cWe have <st data-num=\"08085\" class=\"\">heard</st> <st data-num=\"08089\" class=\"\">reports</st> about them.<p class=\"poetry\"><st data-num=\"03027\" class=\"\">We</st> have <st data-num=\"07503\" class=\"\">become helpless with fear</st>!<n id=\"2\" /> <p class=\"poetry\"><st data-num=\"06869\" class=\"\">Anguish</st> <st data-num=\"02388\" class=\"\">grips</st> us,<p class=\"poetry\"><st data-num=\"02427\" class=\"\">agony</st> like that of a woman <st data-num=\"03205\" class=\"\">giving birth</st> to a baby!</p>",
    "verse": "24"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "Jeremiah",
    "chapter": "6",
    "text": "<p class=\"poetry\">Do <st data-num=\"0408\" class=\"\">not</st> <st data-num=\"03318\" class=\"\">go out</st> into the <st data-num=\"07704\" class=\"\">countryside</st>.<p class=\"poetry\">Do <st data-num=\"0408\" class=\"\">not</st> <st data-num=\"01980\" class=\"\">travel</st> on the <st data-num=\"01870\" class=\"\">roads</st>.<p class=\"poetry\"><st data-num=\"03588\" class=\"\">For</st> the <st data-num=\"0341\" class=\"\">enemy</st> is there with <st data-num=\"02719\" class=\"\">sword</st> in hand.<n id=\"1\" /> <p class=\"poetry\">They are spreading <st data-num=\"04032\" class=\"\">terror</st> <st data-num=\"05439\" class=\"\">everywhere</st>.\u201d<n id=\"2\" /> </p>",
    "verse": "25"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "Jeremiah",
    "chapter": "6",
    "text": "<p class=\"poetry\">So I said,<n id=\"1\" /> \u201cOh, my <st data-num=\"01323\" class=\"\">dear</st> <st data-num=\"05971\" class=\"\">people</st>,<n id=\"2\" /> <st data-num=\"02296\" class=\"\">put on</st> <st data-num=\"08242\" class=\"\">sackcloth</st><p class=\"poetry\">and <st data-num=\"06428\" class=\"\">roll</st> in <st data-num=\"0665\" class=\"\">ashes</st>.<p class=\"poetry\"><st data-num=\"060 06213\">Mourn</st> with <st data-num=\"08563\" class=\"\">painful</st> <st data-num=\"04553\" class=\"\">sobs</st><p class=\"poetry\">as though you had lost your <st data-num=\"03173\" class=\"\">only child</st>.<p class=\"poetry\"><st data-num=\"03588\" class=\"\">For</st> <st data-num=\"06597\" class=\"\">any moment now</st><n id=\"3\" /> that <st data-num=\"07703\" class=\"\">destructive army</st><n id=\"4\" /> <p class=\"poetry\">will <st data-num=\"0935\" class=\"\">come</st> <st data-num=\"05921\" class=\"\">against</st> us.\u201d</p>",
    "verse": "26"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "Jeremiah",
    "chapter": "6",
    "text": "<p class=\"bodytext\">The <span class=\"smcaps\">Lord</span> said to me,<n id=\"1\" /> <p class=\"poetry\">\u201cI have <st data-num=\"05414\" class=\"\">made</st> you like a <st data-num=\"0969\" class=\"\">metal assayer</st><p class=\"poetry\">to test my <st data-num=\"05971\" class=\"\">people</st> like ore.<n id=\"2\" /> <p class=\"poetry\">You are to <st data-num=\"03045\" class=\"\">observe</st> them<p class=\"poetry\">and <st data-num=\"0974\" class=\"\">evaluate</st> <st data-num=\"01870\" class=\"\">how</st> they <st data-num=\"01870\" class=\"\">behave</st>.\u201d<n id=\"3\" /> </p>",
    "verse": "27"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "Jeremiah",
    "chapter": "6",
    "text": "<p class=\"bodytext\">I reported,<n id=\"1\" /> <p class=\"poetry\">\u201c<st data-num=\"03605\" class=\"\">All</st> of them are the most <st data-num=\"05493\" class=\"\">stubborn</st> of <st data-num=\"05637\" class=\"\">rebels</st>!<n id=\"2\" /> <p class=\"poetry\">They are as hard as <st data-num=\"05178\" class=\"\">bronze</st> or <st data-num=\"01270\" class=\"\">iron</st>.<p class=\"poetry\">They <st data-num=\"01980\" class=\"\">go about</st> <st data-num=\"07400\" class=\"\">telling lies</st>.<p class=\"poetry\"><st data-num=\"01992\" class=\"\">They</st> <st data-num=\"03605\" class=\"\">all</st> <st data-num=\"07843\" class=\"\">deal corruptly</st>. </p>",
    "verse": "28"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "Jeremiah",
    "chapter": "6",
    "text": "<p class=\"poetry\">The <st data-num=\"0800\" class=\"\">fiery</st> <st data-num=\"04647\" class=\"\">bellows</st> of judgment burn fiercely.<p class=\"poetry\">But there is too much <st data-num=\"05777\" class=\"\">dross</st> to be <st data-num=\"0784 08552\">removed</st>.<n id=\"1\" /> <p class=\"poetry\">The <st data-num=\"06884\" class=\"\">process</st> of <st data-num=\"06884\" class=\"\">refining</st> them has <st data-num=\"07723\" class=\"\">proved useless</st>.<n id=\"2\" /> <p class=\"poetry\">The <st data-num=\"07451\" class=\"\">wicked</st> have <st data-num=\"03808\" class=\"\">not</st> been <st data-num=\"05423\" class=\"\">purged</st>. </p>",
    "verse": "29"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "Jeremiah",
    "chapter": "6",
    "text": "<p class=\"poetry\">They are <st data-num=\"07121\" class=\"\">regarded</st> as \u2018<st data-num=\"03988\" class=\"\">rejected</st> <st data-num=\"03701\" class=\"\">silver</st>\u2019<n id=\"1\" /> <p class=\"poetry\"><st data-num=\"03588\" class=\"\">because</st> the <span class=\"smcaps\"><st data-num=\"03068\" class=\"\">Lord</st></span> <st data-num=\"03988\" class=\"\">rejects</st> them.\u201d</p>",
    "verse": "30"
  }
]